Quickstrike:



"Nice shot," Quickstrike said when he saw the body of the alien fall. 
He looked to Black Arachnia. "Remind me not t'--" He turned his head 
around to hear Dark Mouse. He frowned and turned to the rodent. He 
narrowed his crimson optics from his distance and jogged off to her. 
He bent down with his odd, mismatched hands on his knees, and 
said, "What are ya doin'? Ya bailin' us?"
